{"tid":2154371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獲中大取錄　狀元黃摯毅憂新聞及言論自由逐步削弱 香港現時的情況比一個月前更沒有曙光","createTime":"2020-08-13T05:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T06:46:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"45733db512641127974cb6289d493c62c04a7c63","tid":2154371,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:44:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543483-20200813.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543483-20200813.htm&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=5b558058\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543483-20200813.htm&h=861d44fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543483-20200813.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n大學聯招結果公布，4萬多名申請人中，有15642人，即約37%獲派教資會資助的學士學位課程。另外，今年有7名狀元，4名狀元獲港大取錄，另一名狀元黃摯毅獲中大理學院取錄。<br />\n<br />\n黃摯毅接受本台訪問表示，香港現時的情況比一個月前，即文憑試放榜時更沒有曙光，壹傳媒被搜查及多人被捕，令他擔心香港的新聞及言論自由會逐步削弱。他說，入讀中大理學院是因為對腦神經有興趣，但會考慮中途轉到外國升學，因為外國的研究較香港好，而香港的「紅線」不斷移動，擔心4年後香港人會否被禁止出境。對於現時的大學學生會或學會都會就政治議題發聲，考慮參加生物學會的黃摯毅說，在現時情況下，寧願站在背後，都不願意「站出來」，擔心「槍打出頭鳥」，影響日後到外國做研究工作，但強調一定會關注社會事件。<br />\n<br />\n他又形容香港以往是一個漂亮的湖，有豐盛的魚產，但現時湖水突然被抽乾，湖中的魚「相濡以沫、垂死掙扎」，又指香港人的肉體可能會繼續生存，但靈魂可能就快死亡。"},{"pid":"ba9224f17a3ce04c382762729719ad0bc684e9b4","tid":2154371,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d120b056c7cbc304e3995495cd4a667863b08f49","tid":2154371,"uid":318720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"『香港人的肉體可能會繼續生存，但靈魂可能就快死亡』"},{"pid":"92b139d8a1e72f64b291e7ed18344e550f2e98ae","tid":2154371,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d120b056c7cbc304e3995495cd4a667863b08f49","tid":2154371,"uid":318720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"『香港人的肉體可能會繼續生存，但靈魂可能就快死亡』"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef7c0c470d6a788c7a4c080c3f6f19e5fda5783","tid":2154371,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d120b056c7cbc304e3995495cd4a667863b08f49","tid":2154371,"uid":318720,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:46:59.000Z","msg":"『香港人的肉體可能會繼續生存，但靈魂可能就快死亡』"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa48c418b4d470d4666272c6b662144e8c512e4f","tid":2154371,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:50:59.000Z","msg":"都答得幾好"},{"pid":"1abd1e9bd84a0d2356a8a559315f87e2d8f4bbb8","tid":2154371,"uid":34047,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"難得一個會講心裡話既狀元<br />\n通精都係避重就輕以唔得失人就目標"},{"pid":"2fc673b8df64c50da89662f0e65e27f1a9370f66","tid":2154371,"uid":318720,"like"